code: @Override public List<ServiceDefinition> apply(List<ServiceDefinition> services) {     for (int i = 0. i < delegatesSize. i++) {         services = delegates.get(i).apply(services).     }     return services. }
// ********************** // Helpers // ********************** public static CombinedServiceFilter wrap(ServiceFilter... delegates) {     return new CombinedServiceFilter(Arrays.asList(delegates)). }
